edBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T07:08:37.000Z","msg":"Copy重點，全篇文章可以入Link睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《幸福不及》由李榮浩作曲，葛大為作詞。2017年容祖兒擔任李榮浩香港演唱會嘉賓時獲得承諾寫歌回贈，過了一年李榮浩沒忘承諾說到做到，不但量身寫歌更在北京錄音室相約帶美食探班，讓祖兒印象深刻！這首三拍的歌曲在編曲與節奏上都帶有頹廢、慵懶的藍調味道，除了由李榮浩譜曲更有葛大為量身寫詞，兩位金曲才子的助攻打造特別風情讓這首歌在專輯里相對的讓人玩味，同時這也是一首難度偏高不好上手詮釋的歌，需將技巧拋諸腦后慢慢沈淀下來憑感覺而唱，唱完還要慢慢想，想完又再唱出另一種感覺，連這張專輯也是一路慢慢籌備製作慢慢唱，無招勝有招的歌唱嘗試，也讓一向不敢松懈的容祖兒開始學著停下來慢慢想，學會讓時間帶著自己尋找解答。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.fansyes.com/Content/20181019/kpkkrwwfj50jo.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.fansyes.com%2FContent%2F20181019%2Fkpkkrwwfj50jo.shtml&d=CibHFg8IZnIlajm27DXBW2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9f761314\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.fansyes.com/Content/20181019/kpkkrwwfj50jo.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"b07a05bd7ef7f603f866c2b1a04b6b9a8f4efca0","tid":853793,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e258d120aab76db1eb319cd4c67fb1ca5bedad59","tid":853793,"uid":72633,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人買左？<br />\n我係popular 話冇poster<br />\n想知係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb5570fa8c2984590f6d183b3e58951f5d602fad","tid":853793,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e258d120aab76db1eb319cd4c67fb1ca5bedad59","tid":853793,"uid":72633,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人買左？<br />\n我係popular 話冇poster<br />\n想知係咪真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"暫時上網見到CD Warehouse有<br />\n其他無人講"},{"pid":"c19454d0b47d304f30a629e710af77ff20723792","tid":853793,"uid":57141,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T